description:
A dynamic action game that immerses the player in the world of tank battles. Take command of a powerful tank and go on exciting missions full of dangers!

Each level is a unique battlefield where the player will have to perform a variety of combat missions. During these missions you will face different types of enemies: from lightly armored vehicles to heavy assault tanks. Plan your attacks, use cover, strategically maneuver and destroy your enemies to achieve victory on every battlefield.

Fight against numerous opponents, complete difficult tasks and prove that you are the real hero of the armored forces!

GAME FEATURES:
• Stylized cartoon graphics;
• Many levels with varying difficulty;
• Exciting gameplay for fans of tank battles;
• Atmospheric sound;
